item.title: CVE-2021-26614|2024-08-03T20:26:25.515Z -- efm%20networks%20%26%20multimedia -- iptime%20c200%20ip%20camera
item.description: ius_get.cgi in IpTime C200 camera allows remote code execution. A remote attacker may send a crafted parameters to the exposed vulnerable web service interface which invokes the arbitrary shell command.
